content: bertux: Contributed to dependency management by updating viem versions in PR #1637 (+109/-48 lines) and proposed a new Fuse plugin through PR #2341 and issue #3002. Created issue #1635 regarding outdated Viem versions for Arthera EVM chain support, which was subsequently closed. Made significant code changes across 320 files (+40486/-30149 lines) in 17 commits, with activity concentrated on a few days this month and primarily focused on configuration files (36%) and code (32%).
